{"tid":659820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心玻璃心碎！ 外媒分析和中國做生意5大地雷","createTime":"2018-05-10T07:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T12:20:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eecae56a96d368ab914daf0795fc6ad72590ceff","tid":659820,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"小心玻璃心碎！ 外媒分析和中國做生意5大地雷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2421294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2421294&d=PptU2tuoabB7ai56lLI6Gm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1fc1b402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2421294&h=f115a743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2421294</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕許多企業將中國視為掏金地，但從過往案例來看似乎地雷不少，像是航空公司被要求更改台、港、澳標註，或是蘋果遭到內容審查。外媒指出，想跟中國做生意，需要滿足其一大串條件。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN Money》整理出與中國做生意的5大妥協：<br />\n<br />\n首先，<span style=\"color: red;\">「你如何談論台灣、香港和澳門」</span>。中國將台灣視為其領土的一部分，香港和澳門則是中國的特別行政區，當中國發現外國公司將台港澳視為獨立，就會採取行動，今年1月萬豪酒店因為將台港澳各自視為國家，遭中國封鎖網頁，美航空業與ZARA也面臨類似問題。<br />\n<br />\n第二，<span style=\"color: red;\">「數據傳輸遭到限制」</span>。去年6月，中國頒布法令，加強管制數據傳輸，並要求關鍵數據要儲存在中國，被外界批評是監控訊息的手段。有部分外國企業對此妥協，像是蘋果把中國客戶的雲端資料存在一間中國貴州的國有企業。<br />\n<br />\n第三，<span style=\"color: red;\">「必須與當地企業合資」</span>。中國限制部分行業的外國公司，必須與中國企業合資才能在中國經營。包括通用汽車、豐田汽車、高通、英特爾等企業，均與當地企業合資以通過規定。此一經濟運作是美中貿易戰的爭論點之一，美國政府認為中方可藉此得到知識產權。<br />\n<br />\n第四，<span style=\"color: red;\">「談到達賴喇嘛時要小心」</span>。達賴喇嘛在全球都受到歡迎，除了中國以外，中國認為他是一個需要被譴責的分裂分子。<br />\n<br />\n最後是<span style=\"color: red;\">「內容審查」</span>。中國對於網路公司有著嚴格的內容審查規定，蘋果、LinkedIn等跨國大企業均吃過虧。"},{"pid":"bd4c52c373641f710b31804c57b05d5356aa385d","tid":659820,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb3dd9947e06984a09c73fc5cc0e02b448358e4","tid":659820,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d729fcf73430fef0d79d3a394c43a4824b0f611b","tid":659820,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"達賴喇嘛在全球都受到歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9cbe6cda0210ba84c217495e74be23a61025e2","tid":659820,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75a4e325d7d02eadc110afdf05b869da877a173","tid":659820,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777bbfe79292eb438d48b04a23a21eac1bc3aebc","tid":659820,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"其實都已經係公開嘅秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c14ba5be032552313b446dfff87bddf17ad6eb7","tid":659820,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a3b7142329d5a2618fffcfa34da2e87d2fcb03","tid":659820,"uid":48526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:20:19.000Z","msg":"仲未講賺錢都匯唔走<br />\n<br />\n要俾枱底錢先有可能拿到牌照<br />\n<br />\n生意做得大啲，老共就要插自己黨員入董事局，唔係就冇運行等等，都幾厚道。"}]}